channel.title: Please Help!
channel.description: :mad: :mad: Omg ! i'm trying to add more shops and edit my teleports but i have no client.java file . I downloaded a source that already had a shops and teleports edited into it and they all work fine but i cannot add any more shops and i cannot edit the teleports!! Does anyone know where i should go to edit these becase i have no client.java file .. :(

item.title: Please Help!
item.dc:creator: @x1_att_ftw_x x1 att ftw x
item.description:
@x1_att_ftw_x wrote:

maybe try going in data/cfg/spawn-config, there you can find the npc coords and change where they spawn

if you want to change teleports go into clickingbuttens.java
This is located in Src/Server/Model/Players/Packets/ClickingButtons

open that file then goin to ur server and click home teleport and see what it says
then search the case by pressing ctrl F (case ###)
